var http = require("https");

var options = {
  "method": "POST",
  "hostname": "becandid.com",
  "port": null,
  "path": "/api/add_comment",
  "headers": {
    "//host": "becandid.com",
    "//user-agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0",
    "//accept": "*/*",
    "//accept-language": "en-US,en;q=0.5",
    "//referer": "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY",
    "//content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
    "//candid-encoded": "1",
    "cookie": "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==",
    "//dnt": "1",
    "//connection": "keep-alive",
    "//pragma": "no-cache",
    "//cache-control": "no-cache"
  }
};

var req = http.request(options, function (res) {
  var chunks = [];

  res.on("data", function (chunk) {
    chunks.push(chunk);
  });

  res.on("end", function () {
    var body = Buffer.concat(chunks);
    console.log(body.toString());
  });
});

req.write("ak5AwoFrTUB3YUs3woFWS1w5VUtcOFF0VX1pXjhzaXVZbWtOXTtrSzhSa19VN1FbUH5gWlzCgFRPWXNqOlhzVHFJcWk5OHthXjw3UXRhwoBoXl18YU9VbWFOc8KBYF5RemFeWEBrT1E4XVVCQw==");
req.end();

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/add_comment"

	payload := strings.NewReader("ak5AwoFrTUB3YUs3woFWS1w5VUtcOFF0VX1pXjhzaXVZbWtOXTtrSzhSa19VN1FbUH5gWlzCgFRPWXNqOlhzVHFJcWk5OHthXjw3UXRhwoBoXl18YU9VbWFOc8KBYF5RemFeWEBrT1E4XVVCQw==")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")

	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/edit_comment"

	payload := strings.NewReader("YDlAe2leXXxrTUB3YUs3woBVwoFYPFVLUDxVcGFxaTk4e2FePDdfOllzbE9YQFp1XcKBa0pcwoBUTkxzVHFJN2FfVTdRW1B+YDlAe2leXXxrSjtE")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/delete_comment"

	payload := strings.NewReader("YDlAe2leXXxrTUB3YUs3woBVwoFYPFVLUDxVbkRE")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")

	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")

	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")

var options = {
  "method": "POST",
  "hostname": "becandid.com",
  "port": null,
  "path": "/api/report_comment",
  "headers": {
    "//host": "becandid.com",
    "//user-agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0",
    "//accept": "*/*",
    "//accept-language": "en-US,en;q=0.5",
    "//referer": "https://becandid.com/me/posts",
    "//content-type": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8",
    "//candid-encoded": "1",
    "cookie": "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==",
    "//dnt": "1",
    "//connection": "keep-alive",
    "//pragma": "no-cache",
    "//cache-control": "no-cache"
  }
};

var req = http.request(options, function (res) {
  var chunks = [];

  res.on("data", function (chunk) {
    chunks.push(chunk);
  });

  res.on("end", function () {
    var body = Buffer.concat(chunks);
    console.log(body.toString());
  });
});

req.write("YDlAe2leXXxrTUB3YUs3woBVwoFYPFVxYH9USmHCgGFeTcKBaTk7QGk5YXRrTkB+aF5URA==");
req.end();

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/report_comment"

	payload := strings.NewReader("YDlAe2leXXxrTUB3YUs3woBVwoFYPFVxYH9USmHCgGFeTcKBaTk7QGk5YXRrTkB+aF5URA==")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/me/posts")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/edit_post"

	payload := strings.NewReader("ak5AwoFrTUB3YUs3woFWS1w5VUtcOFF0VW9qT1l3aTk7QFp1XcKBa0pcwoBUTkxzVHFJN2FfVTdRW1B+ak5AwoFrSkxE")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/mute_post"

	payload := strings.NewReader("ak5AwoFrTUB3YUs3woFWS1w5VUtcOA==")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"strings"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/post_comments"

	payload := strings.NewReader("aF48cWlPXXJhXUBxaTk4e2FePDdqwoE3woBRdVl2anRdb2FOXXJXW0x0ak5AwoFrTUB3YUs3woFWS1w5VUtcOA==")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/post/YfWlEoPmuhY")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

  "method": "GET",
  "hostname": "becandid.com",
  "port": null,
  "path": "/api/get_activity",
  "headers": {
    "//host": "becandid.com",
    "//user-agent": "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0",
    "//accept": "*/*",
    "//accept-language": "en-US,en;q=0.5",
    "//referer": "https://becandid.com/me/signup",
    "//candid-encoded": "1",
    "cookie": "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==",
    "//dnt": "1",
    "//connection": "keep-alive",
    "//content-length": "0"
  }
};

var req = http.request(options, function (res) {
  var chunks = [];

  res.on("data", function (chunk) {
    chunks.push(chunk);
  });

  res.on("end", function () {
    var body = Buffer.concat(chunks);
    console.log(body.toString());
  });
});

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/get_activity"

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("GET", url, nil)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/me/signup")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//content-length", "0")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

package main

import (
	"fmt"
	"net/http"
	"io/ioutil"
)

func main() {

	url := "https://becandid.com/api/start_upload"

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("GET", url, nil)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/feed/new")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")
	req.Header.Add("//pragma", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//cache-control", "no-cache")
	req.Header.Add("//content-length", "0")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
	body, _ := ioutil.ReadAll(res.Body)

	fmt.Println(res)
	fmt.Println(string(body))

}

	payload := strings.NewReader("a19Vc2pzQHdhSzd+UXRzfGA5fzhhTl1tYDlAe2leXXxrT1RAVHBhN2hPUXNgXllzYUs3fw==")

	req, _ := http.NewRequest("POST", url, payload)

	req.Header.Add("//host", "becandid.com")
	req.Header.Add("//user-agent", "Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.3; Win64; x64; rv:53.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/53.0")
	req.Header.Add("//accept", "*/*")
	req.Header.Add("//accept-language", "en-US,en;q=0.5")
	req.Header.Add("//referer", "https://becandid.com/me/signup")
	req.Header.Add("//content-type", "application/x-www-form-urlencoded; charset=UTF-8")
	req.Header.Add("//candid-encoded", "1")
	req.Header.Add("cookie", "s=!hnjqCEiFJBC7y+SGjTt+Lw==?gAJVAXN9cQFVBmV4cF9pZE0nCnOGcQIu;u=!s2WPwYW5ht6fJI6PTxASHw==?gAJVAXVVBjgzMDM3MnEBhnECLg==")
	req.Header.Add("//dnt", "1")
	req.Header.Add("//connection", "keep-alive")

	res, _ := http.DefaultClient.Do(req)

	defer res.Body.Close()
